rows.label: qev060611_MSG0001
rows.name:
You were watching that fight with Orleron from the
sidelines, weren't you? You must think me awful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060611_SEL0011
rows.name: Point out where you feel Vera spoke too harshly.

rows.label: qev060611_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Vera that you see nothing awful about her.

rows.label: qev060611_MSG0002
rows.name:
Yeah, well, you're entitled to your opinions.
I didn't want to be that harsh, honestly,
but the dude refuses to take a hint![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060611_MSG0003
rows.name:
...But I am. I broke his little heart, I just know it.
I'm the worst ever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060611_MSG0004
rows.name:
I didn't want to be that harsh, but the dude just refuses
to take a hint![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060611_MSG0005
rows.name: I just want to live free, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060611_MSG0006
rows.name:
I don't want to spend my life tied down and stressing
over all his baggage![ST:wait ]
